 italic;"&gt;&lt;em style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.4; font-style: italic;"&gt;摄影师：法新社/盖蒂图片社&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;一艘探险游轮上&lt;strong style="font-size: 16px;"&gt;爆发的汉坦病毒&lt;/strong&gt;已导致三名乘客死亡，另外五人患病，目前已蔓延至各大洲。随着调查人员竞相追查其来源，该事件&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/9e8oOr6DcczaoIsdntI5C_qG98WtXi98tpMWYVtyt2GkdJ5lyOLT3zJzGgHLzLqpTkUf-STOQTGU7JFE6GVsQlODbpsjH8hRq96FbfansngBGOsUZ60H-bl8mRoMxD45Re5fKca4SS6H0xHwh3iTqo7lFJk4X-SFaICfWdELOQDwtdpI7dQiKvvqRmpbI_k28cWoBpwUL1AiEkjPGGfTjFgWfWVByYGAVJxPtui6dhoAW05-xcwAvOcWfGycnJpB0GDNgiNVRb_fZLaCI0EzxFPZF9Sm4iHxmk4sTqKKXYcEgMnwlV0-iqWOqTW_lQ1myCpbLbkI-vQcgFL3rW7gFEuEOqmoaGRMl1S7QmGpEJaGnArdm2hQ37mdRqMFucc2ESLXJJ3AXJihRUTamFF_lMPiinQRzmlM1zS98QJgt66KMJZ47E2cy6L6MxHC1K7AESNf2NjWLx4xli6TLz77hjQ7HR1p-CCNUeu8aS2tieg3jw8VD4uceHXD2VEZexOmehtu2JKW8Uq2-EMTuDNEyOBOg74WtEkGIC7t_1xk7cdnlx7JpoPrFw/cOqJnZCq_KKnvTFyeG0HLUbnFuffCYE4/20" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="致命的游轮爆发暴露了旅行的盲点"&gt;暴露了病毒检测中的一个关键盲点&lt;/a&gt;。 &lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul style="margin-top: 24px; padding-inline-start: 24px;"&gt;&lt;li style="font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; line-height: 1.4; font-size: 16px;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-size: 16px;"&gt;在穿越一些最偏远、野生动物丰富的地区的小船上&lt;/strong&gt;， &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/FWlRoAaFr5ZapzwEJ6gIWsi7FNaQXjISFSBAzFMxLl9vTZ9MpN0FcEgD6XcgdGMQkP8GDGkJJJsTjpIVV2E7LhHgsRukwo06Mf8R9anGCk0xIN6rB3LUaFUseoB-RV8yiGJhEy-erL2_1jRAra7WFN04N3nEcjjKHRiz8xwbWFHD1nKyzNqJXPnTNwA8Ce8E8AwC1A10pdw0Fkgg_nASNwQLVEiifLg4Vnmlg-vUGresVJWhGN_7L9vQ3klfxJYmw9WM3PTjeOu9Yj2-Fnqi4tUmY_jmNVnaca3YClSgA0S9gTb2MgJLa08W0RM9vfl019IH-gGt6zRWAlgIwcy3O1fHq6b6b6pEJrHYawC7EvuTV_Zv2uAN63Wegl-RhKuzPyLrVR1v51hXwk_Tvu7DngeOuwdtdqUymERw6yPQOjZamfMUcYODM7hDvgTZUp7xZY3cVjnRs4jinx848jTCnGlklsEVYc_RltROl5kpcbORvvwjB4aTLkZYzP9x1BeBWyyCPW9wmhfU_f29Qgfar-ibxtTpoFeprjkTQGYsdDsP39LYbG3I-qlb-vTo0w/dHhIoQoX43HQItkJqAQfpTHYLNbcuFWV/2